Package: regSim
Type: Package
Title: YPR and SPR Interactive Shiny App
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Dave", family = "Smith", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "fish.dzs0017@gmail.com")
Description: An interactive Shiny application for yield-per-recruit (YPR) and
    spawning potential ratio (SPR) analysis in age-structured fish population
    models. Includes exported modeling functions for growth, vulnerability,
    simulation, summary statistics, and yield-curve analysis.
